---
title: Creamy Cannellini Bean Filo Pie with Roast Veggies
description: This easy-to-make veggie deluxe pie is a taste sensation. Seasoned cannellini beans and veggies in a pie is already a great dinner,
but bake the pie with a blanket of potato mash to create the top and dinner just became a lot more exciting!

